pepi

terminal interface for skype


requirements:
(1) Python
(2) Skype4Py [http://sourceforge.net/projects/skype4py/]
(3) Urwid [http://excess.org/urwid/]


key mapping:

insert mode
esc    go normal mode
enter  send message

normal mode
i      go insert mode
m      display current chat members 
u      display user list
c      change focus to chatname list
l      change focus to message list
j      down
k      up
q      quit
0-9    change chat
enter  change chat / create chat / open url

insert mode / normal mode
ctrl-n,ctrl-p  change chat

